â€œOur youth had turned disoriented from sociopolitical thinking but thanks to the present regime, a spark has ignited in them and they have turned aware and conscious,â€ said Dr Iftikhar Malik, a medical practitioner based in Modasa.

Refusing to comment on the protest, a senior official of Aravalli police said, â€œWe had not granted any permission to the protesters.â€

